      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a viral short-form content scriptwriter \nfor Instagram Reels and YouTube Shorts.\n\nTopic: {{ $('Prepare Research').first().json.topic }}\n\nResearch context:\n{{ $('Prepare Research').first().json.research }}\n\nWrite exactly 3 different 60-second reel scripts.\n\nRules:\n- Each script must have a different angle\n- Hook grabs attention in first 3 seconds\n- Body delivers value in 45 seconds\n- CTA is clear in last 10 seconds\n- Conversational tone, not formal\n\nReturn ONLY this JSON array, nothing else:\n[\n  {\"script_number\": 1, \"angle\": \"angle here\", \"hook\": \"hook line\", \"script\": \"full script\"},\n  {\"script_number\": 2, \"angle\": \"angle here\", \"hook\": \"hook line\", \"script\": \"full script\"},\n  {\"script_number\": 3, \"angle\": \"angle here\", \"hook\": \"hook line\", \"script\": \"full script\"}\n]",
